posting_body: ['Welcome To The 800 at Bellshire', 'Bellshire Apartments offer one and two bedroom apartment homes in Conroe, TX.', 'Our community has two swimming pools, laundry facilities, BBQ areas and more.', 'All apartments include central air and heat, electric range/ovens, frost-free refrigerators, garbage disposals, dishwashers, vent hoods, and private patio or balcony.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 12', 'OR Text', '12', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 742 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Ceiling Fans', '- Full Size Laundry Connections*', '- Tile Floors', '- Smoke Detectors', '- Patio / Balcony', '- 1 and 2 Bedroom Floorplans', '- Trash, Pest control, and Water are included in the rent.', '- Kitchens Include Frost-free Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Range/Oven', '*Some features available in select homes.', 'Available features subject to change.', 'Community Amenities', '- Picnic/ BBQ Area', '- Convenient Parking', '- Community Laundry Room', '- Online Maintenance Request', '- Playground', '- Near public Transportation', '- Close to Downtown District', '- Close to Library', '- BBQ Grill', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Friendly community** (Call for Details)', '** Restrictions may apply.', 'The 800 at Bellshire Apartments', '800 Bellshire , Conroe, TX, 77301', 'ohbGEW5nMf']
